
Installation
------------

Prerequisites:

 - LibXML (http://xmlsoft.org/downloads.html)
 - Python 2.4 or newer (www.python.org)
 - Twisted framework (http://twistedmatrix.com) - Twisted Core, Twisted Web and Twisted Web 2
   (get them from the SVN trunk)
 - lxml (http://codespeak.net/lxml)
 - python-application

 To enable TLS support, you need:
 - GnuTLS library (http://www.gnu.org/software/gnutls)
 - python-gnutls (http://pypi.python.org/pypi/python-gnutls)

The software has been tested on debian unstable using the following versions:

 - libxml2: 2.6.28.dfsg-1
 - python: 2.4.4-6
 - python-lxml: 1.1.2-1
 - twisted: 2.5.0
 - python-application: 1.0.9
 - python-gnutls: 1.1.1
